overview: In a world where cooking is a televised sport, fry cook Francois Bradshaw is invited to the prestigious Titanium Chef tournament; but he'll have to turn up the heat to triumph over Vladimir Vechnik, the most feared chef in the world.
tagline: In a world where cooking is a televised sport, fry cook Francois Bradshaw is invited to the prestigious Titanium Chef tournament.
title: Titanium Chef
